userPrompt: Build an interactive joke repository with 10,000+ jokes classified by style (dad jokes, knock-knock, puns, riddles, etc.), topic (technology, animals, Disney, Star Wars, etc.), age group (4-6 through 16+), and generation (Gen Alpha, Gen Z, Millennial, Gen X, Boomer). Make it easy to click through with next/prev/random navigation.
researchPlan:
TOPIC: Interactive Joke Repository
STYLES: 8 (Dad Jokes, Knock-Knock, Puns, One-Liners, Riddles, Story, Tongue Twisters, Would You Rather)
TOPICS: 39 across 8 groups (STEM, Nature, Everyday, Movies & Pop Culture, Fantasy, Holidays, Learning, Silly)
AGE GROUPS: 5 tiers (4-6, 7-9, 10-12, 13-15, 16+)
GENERATIONS: 6 (Gen Alpha, Gen Z, Millennial, Gen X, Boomer, Universal)
SECTIONS: Browse (filter + card viewer), Favorites (localStorage), Stats (bar charts)

contentAnalysis.readabilityNote: Interactive joke browser with multi-dimensional filtering, designed for all ages from preschool through adult
